ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[The cumulative number of confirmed human cases of avian influenza
A/(H5N1) since 28 Jan 2004 released by WHO can be viewed at
<http://www.who.int/csr/disease/avian_influenza/country/cases_table_2005_03_11/en/>.
The figures have not been updated since 11 Mar 2005 and remain at 69
cases overall (Cambodia 1, Thailand 17, Viet Nam 51), with 46 deaths
(Cambodia 1, Thailand 12, Viet Nam 33). As of 25 Mar 2005, only the
figures for Thailand remain valid. - Mod.CP]
